title: Misdirection - Cast No Shadows
description:
One of the best alternative rock bands to come out of Australia for quite some time. These guys have a great rockin sound but also mix it up with some awesome melodic tracks too, making it one of the most dynamic and interesting albums I&#039;ve listened to in ages!

If you like Audioslave, Wolfmother, Collective Soul or Fuel, then you&#039;ll love these guys!
